  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "This model has been applied in clinical research contexts involving Class III ventricular assist devices. The CFD hemolysis prediction framework targets the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under VAD operating conditions. Thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated against Model Risk Level 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across key input parameters. The overall assessment outcome is Accepted at Low assurance level, reflecting partial coverage of required credibility gradations. No structured Context of Use object is bound to this unit; the intended-use scope is conveyed through this narrative description only.",
